Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.95,1:06:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被玩了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.95,1:06:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是特别服务喔
