Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.11,1:08:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好忙
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.11,1:08:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想了想
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.12,1:08:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在做坏事
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.12,1:08:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.12,1:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.12,1:08:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.13,1:09:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么顶到我的後背了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.13,1:09:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰到什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.13,1:09:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏东西碰到了
