Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.14,1:09:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.15,1:09:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.15,1:09:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
