Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.29,1:11:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.30,1:11:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.31,1:11:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太近了
