Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.42,1:13:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.42,1:13:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.42,1:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
